text: Cofield Corner is an unincorporated community in Cass Township, Ohio County, in the U.S. state of Indiana. ==Geography== Cofield Corner is located at . It is a hilly forest with multiple small ponds and lakes, located on an intersection of the current State Road 262 and an old farmers lane, which no longer exists. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Ohio County, Indiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Indiana
title: Cofield Corner, Indiana
